Preparing the dataâ¦

df <- df |> distinct(track_name, .keep_all= TRUE)
df <- df |> filter (!grepl("Live at|Live Acoustic", track_name))
df$album_name <- as.character (df$album_name)

Analysis of valence per album:

df$album_name <- as.factor (df$album_name)
ggplot (df, aes(x=album_name, y=valence, color=album_name))+
  geom_boxplot()+
  labs(title="Valence Analysis", x="Album name", y="Valence")+
  scale_x_discrete(guide=guide_axis (n.dodge=5))

Analysis of energy per album:

df$album_name <- as.factor (df$album_name)
ggplot (df, aes(x=album_name, y=energy, color=album_name))+
  geom_boxplot()+
  labs(title="Energy Analysis", x="Album name", y="Energy")+
  scale_x_discrete(guide=guide_axis (n.dodge=5))
